        "zh": "1.工具機硬體設計與規劃<br>2.控制原理<br>3.機電整合與I/O規劃<br>4.軟體控制應用實務<br>5.軟硬體系統整合<br>6.專題實作<br>",
        "en": "1.Tool machine hardware design and planning<br>2.Control principle<br>3.Electromechanical and I/O planning<br>4.Software control application practice<br>5.Software and hardware system integration<br>6.Project practice<br>"
